controllers/brandMappingController.js
Please create this new file in your controllers directory. This file contains the logic for all 7 new APIs:

Get Mapped Brands (for landing page): Fetches brands already configured for an app.

Get Unmapped Brands (for modal): Fetches brands not yet configured for an app.

Get All Platforms (for modal): Gets the full list from v3_t_master_platforms.

Get PBI Dashboards (for sub-modal): Gets Power BI dashboards from v3_t_master_power_bi_dashboard_type.

Get Full Mapping (for edit): Gets all platforms and PBI dashboards for a single brand/app.

Create Full Mapping (for save): A complex transaction to create all mappings.

Delete Full Mapping (for delete): A complex transaction to delete from all 3 tables (as you requested).